&lt;p&gt;Are you a skilled cybersecurity professional who thrives in high-stakes environments and loves solving complex incidents? Do you want to grow your career in a dynamic, global team working with the latest in SecOps tools and threat intelligence? If so, then you might be Fivesky’s next&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SOC Analyst L3!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
